ies srIr nUM prmwqmw dy rihx leI sohxw Gr AwKxw cwhIdw hY, iklHw gVH kihxw cwhIdw hY[
jy gurU dy hukm ivc qur ky prmwqmw dw nwm jpogy qW ies srIr dy AMdroN hI cMgy gux-rUp lwl jvwhr iml jwxgy[
(hy mn!) prmwqmw dw nwm (ihrdy ivc) p`kw kr ky r`K, qW hI ieh srIr ieh pRBU-dw-mMdr bVw sohxw ho skdw hY[
(pr) jo mnu`K Awpxy mn dy mgr qurdy hn auhnW nUM pRBU ny Awp KuMJw id`qw hY auhnW nUM mwieAw dy moh dw Jorw in`q (duKI krdw hY)[
swry jIvW dw mwlk auhI iek prmwqmw hY, pr imldw pUrI iksmq nwl hY ]11]
