(Asl) ivrkq auh hY jo auprwmqw nUM sdw kwiem r`Kdw hY,
hr QW mwieAw-rihq pRBU dw invws jwxdw hY;
(Awpxy ihrdy ivc) SWqI qy igAwn dohW nUM iek`Tw krdw hY;
aus ivrkq mnu`K dw srIr (ivkwrW ivc) nhIN if`gdw[
jy gopI cMd (BI ies audwsI dI jugiq vrq ky) siq-srUp pRBU nUM jpy,
qW (ieh gopI cMd BI) prm bRhm ivc lIn ho jwey, ies dw koeI (v`Krw) rUp ryK nwh rih jwey ]4]
