(AslI) nwsqk auh hY jo (prmwqmw dI hsqI nwh mMnx dy QW) srIr nUM Dovy (Bwv, srIr ivcoN pwpW dI hsqI imtw dyvy),
jo Awpxy srIr ivc r`bI joiq jgWdw hY,
su&ny ivc BI vIrj nUM if`gx nhIN dyNdw (Bwv, su&ny ivc BI Awpxy Awp nUM kwm-v`s nhIN hox dyNdw);
